txt.en: 'This will need to get fixed up.'
'The twist in the frame here will be hard to repair.'
'I would venture a look underneath, but I do not trust that rock to hold up.'
'How are repairs progressing on this side?'
'Any concerns with rot or the quality of the boards?'
'Do not forget to double check all the repairs. We do not want this collapsing when we try to put it back up.'
'Lets worry about getting it fixed before we try to figure out moving it.'
'The guards will do their jobs, make sure you do yours.'
'At this rate, we are not ever going to finish the repairs, so quit your worrying.'
'You figured out how we are going to patch this gap yet?'
'Keep up the work, bit by bit we will get this wheel repaired.'
